      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/sqa-mrl2",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2024 R1) is subject to vendor-maintained software quality assurance procedures including version-controlled releases, regression test suites covering blood-analog flow benchmarks, and documented change logs. SQA documentation reviewed and found compliant with FDA guidance on software validation for simulation tools at MRL 2."
    },
    {
